          "date": "2013-07-04 23:57:30.000000000",
          "tz": 480
        },
        "subject": "LU-3335 scrub: convert filter_fid_old to LMA",
        "message": "LU-3335 scrub: convert filter_fid_old to LMA\n\nThe OI scrub will generate FID-in-LMA for old OST-object, which will\nunify OSD behaviors. To make LMA to fit into the 256-byte OST inode,\nit will shrink the filter_fid_old as filter_fid, and the parent FID\nwill be kept.\n\nSigned-off-by: Fan Yong <fan.yong@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I49cee18ee479fc33dab40b490480a1f292eeacdf\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
